                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi> I produce a certificate of Swain's former conviction at this court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 23<hi rend="italic">rd Nov</hi>, 1846, <hi rend="italic">confined six months</hi>)—the prisoner Swain is the person.</p>
